    "verify": "kotoba-auth eth/btc/cacao + Ed25519 (ADR-2605262130) — never reimplemented (Shannon)",
    "confidentiality": "XChaCha20-Poly1305 + Signal-wrapped per-recipient keys (ADR-2605181100)",
